Introduction
------------

This directory contains the entire source code for the frontend. Simply
put, the frontend is a SPA, which means a single HTML page handles everything
through JavaScript.

For more information about development, build, and deployment, please read
the wiki in this repository.

Q and A
--------

1. The first question that might come to your mind is why I use direct
   DOM manipulation.

It’s because of performance, and I want to be as close to the DOM as
possible to maintain tight control over performance and the codebase’s
direction.
